Day 7: 2-to-4 Decoder
A 2-to-4 Decoder takes 2 input lines and activates exactly one of the 4 outputs, based on the input combination.  
It also has an enable (EN) signal to control activation.

- Inputs: 2 (a1, a0)
- Outputs: 4 (y3, y2, y1, y0)
- Enable: 1 (en)

 Truth Table

| EN | A1 | A0 | Y3 Y2 Y1 Y0 |
|----|----|----|-------------|
| 0  |  X |  X | 0000        |
| 1  |  0 |  0 | 0001        |
| 1  |  0 |  1 | 0010        |
| 1  |  1 |  0 | 0100        |
| 1  |  1 |  1 | 1000        |

